longName: Home Product Center Public Company Limited
longBusinessSummary: Home Product Center Public Company Limited operates as a home improvement retailer in Thailand and Malaysia. The company trades in a range of goods and materials for construction, addition, refurbishment, renovation, and improvement of buildings, houses, and residences; and provides a range of related services. It also offers 3D, installation, maintenance, home makeover, warehousing, and distribution services. In addition, the company rents space. As of December 31, 2020, it had 115 branches. The company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Nonthaburi, Thailand.
